\f0\b\fs40 \cf2 \cb3 \strokec2 \uc0\u55356 \u57273  1. SuperCollider Code (Lower Octave)\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f3\i\b0\fs32 \cf2 Run this first in SuperCollider.
\f1\i0 \
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

